\[
G = 1 \, \text{T}, \quad f = \frac{Bq}{2\pi m} = \frac{1 \times 1.6 \times 10^{-19}}{2\pi \times 4.0026 \times 1.66 \times 10^{-27}}
\]

Calculating the frequency \( f \):
\[
f = 3.83 \times 10^6 \, \text{Hz} = 3.83 \, \text{MHz}
\]

